{"tid":565281,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實熱真係好撚恐怖","createTime":"2018-02-18T20:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T07:11:40.000Z","uid":115982,"like":227,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b758008a48f6c8f0f7cead40ba66cc71613714c8","tid":565281,"uid":115982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T20:04:22.000Z","msg":"呢隊波就好似隻厲鬼咁<br />\n無論你邊隊 一年都總會對兩次<br />\n次次見到都打柒你一獲<br />\n用硬朗既踢法踩下你踁骨 <br />\n再震下你ACL <br />\n試下你菠蘿蓋既硬度同外翻能力<br />\n然後再用插水黑哨無視越位你使出真功夫<br />\n唔撚輸都做低你幾件咁<br />\n對住佢就好似比人爆格、老笠咁<br />\n通常都會徒添一和 徒添一敗<br />\n或者留低幾條韌帶咁<br />\n媽呀，熱真係一隊好撚恐怖既波呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd9355e111511d3b65e38e22cf6247d2e44a5d2","tid":565281,"uid":74883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T20:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2692c8ad6dfb9e149fe7d667c81e7d67ba01edd3","tid":565281,"uid":33623,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T21:22:12.000Z","msg":"樓主痢狗"},{"pid":"d55fb528bb494bdbcc8ebd4d56dbaf7f0034d929","tid":565281,"uid":43575,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T21:25:31.000Z","msg":"係，呢幾日又熱番，瞓唔著"},{"pid":"cf0b80cf245a9e5b1872d41e4e485dc135f5f408","tid":565281,"uid":87155,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T22:45:11.000Z","msg":"屌 樓主main 物理治療？"},{"pid":"3f72c23351da4eb3ef9fb9a772e3868f926d55f0","tid":565281,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf0b80cf245a9e5b1872d41e4e485dc135f5f408","tid":565281,"uid":87155,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T22:45:11.000Z","msg":"屌 樓主main 物理治療？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7832f9a564773